uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = FOCUS_OCI and Time > dateRelative(31day) | where substr(formatDate(Time, 'MM/dd/yyyy'), 1, 2) = substr(formatDate(now(), 'MM/dd/yyyy'), 1, 2) | stats sum(oci_AttributedCost) as EUR

'Log Source' = FOCUS_OCI | fields UsageQuantity, -'Host Name (Server)', -'Problem Priority', -Label, -'Entity Type', -'Log Source', -Entity, skuID, oci_CompartmentName, oci_AttributedCost, ResourceName, ResourceId, ServiceName | stats count(oci_AttributedCost) as sc by oci_CompartmentName, subAccountName | top limit = 30 sc
'Log Source' = FOCUS_OCI | stats sum(oci_CostOverage) as EUR | top limit = 20 EUR
'Log Source' = FOCUS_OCI | stats sum(oci_AttributedUsage) as EUR by oci_CompartmentName | top EUR
